<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Add Volunteer</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <!-- <link href="style.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet"> -->
    </head>
    <body style='background-color: rgb(98, 155, 199);'>
        
            <img style='float:left' height= 120 width= 120 src="http://www.sustainablemontereycounty.org/wp-content/uploads/CSMCrefresh/smalllogo.jpg">
            <h1 style='padding-top: 50px'>&emsp;Sign Up To Become A Volunteer</h1>
        <br style='clear:left'>
        <h3>
            Thank you for your interest in volunteering with Communities for Sustainable Monterey 
            County.  Please take a few moments to tell us about yourself and the areas you are 
            interested in contributing your time and talents.
        </h3>
        <form>
            <h3>
                First Name:* <input type='text' id='firstName'>  
                Last Name:* <input type='text' id='lastName'><br>
                Home Phone Number: <input type='text' id='homePhoneNumber'><br> <!-- POSSIBLY ONLY 1 PHONE NUMBER, B/C OF PRIMARY KEY -->
                Mobile Phone Number: <input type='text' id='mobilePhoneNumber'><br>
                Email Address: <input type='text' id='email'><br>
                Facebook ID: <input type='text' id='facebookID'><br>
                Street Address: <input type='text' id='streetAddress'><br>
                City: <input type='text' id='cityAddress'><br>
                State: <input type='text' id='stateAddress'><br>
                Zip Code: <input type='text' id='zipAddress'><br>
            </h3>
            <br>
            <h3>Which CSMC groups would you like to know more about
                or get involved with? (check all that apply)
                <br>
                <input type='checkbox' name='bigSur' value='bigSur'>
                <label for='bigSur'>Big Sur</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='carmel' value='carmel'>
                <label for='carmel'>Carmel</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='marina' value='marina'>
                <label for='marina'>Marina</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='monterey' value='monterey'>
                <label for='monterey'>Monterey</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='pacificGrove' value='pacificGrove'>
                <label for='pacificGrove'>Pacific Grove</label>&emsp;
                <br>
                <input type='checkbox' name='salinas' value='salinas'>
                <label for='salinas'>Salinas</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='seaside' value='seaside'>
                <label for='seaside'>Seaside</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='delReyOaks' value='delReyOaks'>
                <label for='delReyOaks'>Del Rey Oaks</label>&emsp;
                <input type='checkbox' name='general' value='general'>
                <label for='general'>CSMC General</label>
                <br>
                <br>
            </h3>
            <h3>When is the best time to reach you?
                <br>
                Monday: <span style='margin:13px'></span>
                    <input type='checkbox' name='mondayMorning' value='mondayMorning'>
                    <label for='mondayMorning'>Morning</label>&emsp;
                    <input type='checkbox' name='mondayAfternoon' value='mondayAfternoon'>
                    <label for='mondayMorning'>Afternoon</label>&emsp;
                    <input type='checkbox' name='mondayEvening' value='mondayEvening'>
                    <label for='mondayMorning'>Evening</label>
                    <br>
                Tuesday:<span style='margin:13px'></span>
                    <input type='checkbox' name='tuesdayMorning' value='tuesdayMorning'>
                    <label for='tuesdayMorning'>Morning</label>&emsp;
                    <input type='checkbox' name='tuesdayAfternoon' value='tuesdayAfternoon'>
                    <label for='tuesdayMorning'>Afternoon</label>&emsp;
                    <input type='checkbox' name='tuesdayEvening' value='tuesdayEvening'>
                    <label for='tuesdayMorning'>Evening</label>&emsp;
                    <br> 
                Wednesday:
                    <input type='checkbox' name='wednesdayMorning' value='wednesdayMorning'>
                    <label for='tuesdayMorning'>Morning</label>&emsp;
                    <input type='checkbox' name='wednesdayAfternoon' value='wednesdayAfternoon'>
                    <label for='wednesdayMorning'>Afternoon</label>&emsp;
